jodd.madvoc.result

Interface ActionResult<T>

  • All Known Implementing Classes:
    AbstractTemplateViewResult, BaseActionResult, ChainResult, HttpStatusResult, MoveResult, NoneResult, RawResult, ServletDispatcherResult, ServletRedirectResult, ServletUrlRedirectResult, TextResult

    public interface ActionResult<T>
    Action result renders the returned value from an action. Results are singletons for the web application. Results may have a result type, a string identification of the type used when actions return string result.

    • Method Detail

      • getResultName

        java.lang.String getResultName()
        Returns the name of this action result. Returned name can be null for results that does not need to be found using string name identification; i.e. when action does not return a string result.

      • getResultValueType

        java.lang.Class<T> getResultValueType()
        Returns type of result value, passed to the render method and defined by generics. Returns null when this action result does not need to be registered for result value type (eg when used in @Action annotation).

      • render

        void render(ActionRequest actionRequest,
            T resultValue)
     throws java.lang.Exception
        Renders result on given action result value.
        Parameters:
        actionRequest - action request
        resultValue - action method result, may be null
        Throws:
        java.lang.Exception

      • init

        void init()
        Initializes the result.
